flowchart TD
    Start[Phase Complete] --> Validate[gsd-validate-phase]
    Validate --> NyquistCheck[Check Nyquist Principles]
    NyquistCheck --> FindGaps{Gaps Found?}
    FindGaps -- Yes --> GapList[Generate Gap Report]
    GapList --> CreateGaps[gsd-plan-milestone-gaps]
    CreateGaps --> SchedulePhases[Add Remediation Phases to ROADMAP]
    FindGaps -- No --> UAT[gsd-audit-uat]
    
    UAT --> Compare[Compare against REQUIREMENTS.md]
    Compare --> UATGaps{UAT Unmet?}
    UATGaps -- Yes --> ReportUAT[Flag manual test/incomplete criteria]
    UATGaps -- No --> MilestoneAudit[gsd-audit-milestone]
    
    MilestoneAudit --> Archival[gsd-complete-milestone]
    Archival --> Archived[Move Phase state to Archive]
